      <title>日本两次灾难给陷入困境的日本首相带来了新的障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/disasters-in-japan-present-fresh-hurdles-for-troubled-pm-kishida</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于日本首相岸田文雄来说，今年开局不利，毁灭性的地震和致命的飞机失事加剧了他在国内外面临的一系列挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/disasters-in-japan-present-fresh-hurdles-for-troubled-pm-kishida</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 02:00:28 GMT</pubDate>
